---
title: Chicken Satay Kebabs with Basmati Rice and Cucumber Salad
description: Despite satay originating from Indonesia, it is also incredibly popular in the Netherlands (our Dutch menu planning guru Renée LOVES it)! So André (in honour of Renée) created this delicious dish... mildly curried chicken skewers with a zesty cucumber salad and nutty satay sauce. YUM.
